hostage-lior-rudaeff-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-is-held-in-gaza/0000018f-5486-d209-a79f-54afd6b50000</guid></item><item><title>人质、停火谈判将决定拉法行动的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</link><description>以色列军队已经控制了拉​​法边境口岸和费城走廊东部，向哈马斯施压，要求达成人质交易。但这可能会导致对拉法的征服——这有可能导致谈判破裂并危及人质的生命</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何仍能赢得对哈马斯和伊朗的最终胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</link><description>以色列的“单干”战略猛然醒悟：它需要美国和阿拉伯盟友更多的支持来对抗伊朗及其恶毒伙伴，包括哈马斯和真主党。拜登的战后计划提供了这条生命线，但总统还应该添加一个元素</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 18:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</guid></item><item><title>美国缓慢向以色列出售武器引发政策转变问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</link><description>尽管拜登政府实际上已暂停向以色列出售武器，但官员们否认了这标志着政策新转变的说法，尽管美以因迫在眉睫的拉法行动而关系紧张</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列发起拉法行动的威胁奏效了——但主要是针对埃及和美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</link><description>哈马斯的声明开启了达成停火协议的可能性。如果实现的话，也可能影响北部战线，并打开与黎巴嫩外交解决的渠道</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登通过谴责 10 月 7 日的否认主义和美国反犹太主义的高涨来纪念大屠杀日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-holocaust-day-by-condemning-oct-7-denialism-rising-antisemitism-in-america/0000018f-53e7-d4c7-a3af-ffff9ce70000</link><description>拜登在美国国会大厦举行的官方大屠杀纪念仪式上发表主旨演讲时表示，“我们现在不是75年后，而是仅仅七个半月后——人们已经忘记了哈马斯发动了这场恐怖袭击”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:20:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-holocaust-day-by-condemning-oct-7-denialism-rising-antisemitism-in-america/0000018f-53e7-d4c7-a3af-ffff9ce70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列承诺限制拉法行动，将与埃及过境的控制权授予美国私营公司</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-commits-to-limit-rafah-operation-grant-control-of-crossing-to-private-u-s-firm/0000018f-53ee-d6a5-a5ff-d3eeaf700000</link><description>地面入侵拉法之前，以色列在会谈中明确表示，此次行动的目的是在人质谈判中向哈马斯施加压力，并损害该过境点作为哈马斯权力象征的声誉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-commits-to-limit-rafah-operation-grant-control-of-crossing-to-private-u-s-firm/0000018f-53ee-d6a5-a5ff-d3eeaf700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 214 天：以色列代表团抵达埃及进行停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-214-israeli-delegation-lands-in-egypt-for-cease-fire-talks/0000018f-53e0-d6a5-a5ff-d3e075da0001</link><description>以色列国防军控制了拉法过境点的巴勒斯坦一侧 ■ 官员称，以色列代表团抵达埃及继续停火谈判 ■ 以色列总理内塔尼亚胡表示，哈马斯同意的提议与以色列的要求相去甚远，主要区别在于是否会释放活人质或死人质国土报 ■ 辛贝特局长在欧洲歌唱大赛前访问瑞典检查安全程序 ■ 战争结束 214 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 16:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-214-israeli-delegation-lands-in-egypt-for-cease-fire-talks/0000018f-53e0-d6a5-a5ff-d3e075da0001</guid></item><item><title>Telegrass 以色列杂草市场创始人因经营犯罪组织被判 8 年徒刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/telegrass-weed-marketplace-founder-sentenced-to-8-years-for-running-criminal-organization/0000018f-532f-dc9e-a7df-573febbf0000</link><description>经过长达五年的法律斗争，阿莫斯·多夫·西尔弗（Amos Dov Silver）和 Telegrass 的其他员工（该公司成为大麻和其他非法物质的交易渠道）被判犯有一系列毒品交易罪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/telegrass-weed-marketplace-founder-sentenced-to-8-years-for-running-criminal-organization/0000018f-532f-dc9e-a7df-573febbf0000</guid></item><item><title>IDI民意调查发现，大多数以色列人优先考虑哈马斯人质交易而不是拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-prioritize-hamas-hostage-deal-over-rafah-operation-idi-poll-finds/0000018f-5364-dcda-abcf-7b679a700000</link><description>以色列民主研究所的一项民意调查显示，56% 的以色列犹太人和 88% 的阿拉伯人认为，以色列应该优先考虑人质协议而不是拉法攻势——他们中的大多数人都认同政治左翼或中间派观点，而右翼则更喜欢由以色列人发起的军事攻击。薄边距</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/majority-of-israelis-prioritize-hamas-hostage-deal-over-rafah-operation-idi-poll-finds/0000018f-5364-dcda-abcf-7b679a700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队控制了拉法边境口岸的巴勒斯坦一侧，部队在该市东部活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-takes-control-of-palestinian-side-of-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-51eb-d6c3-afdf-5dfbc7980000</link><description>随着人质谈判取得重大进展，以色列国防军已经控制了通往埃及的拉法过境点的巴勒斯坦一侧以及凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，该过境点现已关闭，禁止人道主义援助进入。以色列消息人士向美国有线电视新闻网表示：“这次入侵是一次有限的行动，旨在迫使哈马斯同意达成协议”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:44:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-takes-control-of-palestinian-side-of-rafah-border-crossing/0000018f-51eb-d6c3-afdf-5dfbc7980000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，崇拜圣战之神的犹太极端分子正在变得越来越强大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-israel-jewish-extremists-worshipping-a-god-of-holy-war-are-getting-stronger/0000018f-496c-d17f-adcf-f9ef43630000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列右翼犹太激进分子公然反民主、道德沦丧的政治神学、为巴勒斯坦人的死亡、饥饿和饥饿辩护的世界观正变得更加占主导地位。以色列和世界各地的犹太人必须面对这种对我们传统的亵渎</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 07:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-israel-jewish-extremists-worshipping-a-god-of-holy-war-are-getting-stronger/0000018f-496c-d17f-adcf-f9ef43630000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在真主党无人机袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/0000018f-5169-d6c3-afdf-5d7b6efc0000</link><description>两名预备役军人在黎巴嫩边境梅图拉附近的一次无人机袭击中丧生</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-hezbollah-drone-strike/0000018f-5169-d6c3-afdf-5d7b6efc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡被哈马斯的“是”所困，正在挑拨以色列和美国之间的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trapped-by-hamas-yes-is-driving-a-wedge-between-israel-and-the-u-s/0000018f-4f8f-d17f-adcf-ffef77d50000</link><description>鉴于过去几天的谈判危机，哈马斯宣布接受拟议的停火协议，这让以色列感到意外。 ■ 虽然耶路撒冷不断向埃及派遣代表团，但以色列国防军正在加大军事压力，并在埃及以东开展行动。拉法</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 03:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-trapped-by-hamas-yes-is-driving-a-wedge-between-israel-and-the-u-s/0000018f-4f8f-d17f-adcf-ffef77d50000</guid></item><item><title>美国：以色列同意周三开放凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，向加沙提供援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article-live/hamas-accepts-cease-fire-deal-israel-examining-proposal-idf-enters-rafah-report-claims/0000018f-50c5-df15-a38f-f9d5dba20000</link><description>以色列承诺限制拉法行动，将与埃及过境的控制权授予美国私营公司 ■ 哈马斯代表团也在开罗进行人质谈判 ■ 国防部长加兰特：在消灭哈马斯或释放第一名人质之前，拉法行动不会停止</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 02:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article-live/hamas-accepts-cease-fire-deal-israel-examining-proposal-idf-enters-rafah-report-claims/0000018f-50c5-df15-a38f-f9d5dba20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法政变的策划者在纽约大屠杀纪念仪式上遭到嘲笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/architect-of-israels-judicial-coup-jeered-at-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-in-new-york/0000018f-509c-dcda-abcf-7a9f00050000</link><description>仪式被一群以色列侨民扰乱，他们对西姆查·罗斯曼（来自极右宗教犹太复国主义党的议员）出现在贵宾中感到愤怒</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/architect-of-israels-judicial-coup-jeered-at-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-in-new-york/0000018f-509c-dcda-abcf-7a9f00050000</guid></item><item><title>有多少人质将被释放？以色列与哈马斯之间的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-faces-his-moment-of-truth-after-hamas-accepts-ceasefire-deal/0000018f-4fee-dc9e-a7df-4ffe493a0000</link><description>哈马斯的提议包括首先释放 33 名人质，无论是“死是活”，每周释放 3 名人质 ■ 以色列坚持释放 33 名人质，每三天释放 3 名人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 22:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-faces-his-moment-of-truth-after-hamas-accepts-ceasefire-deal/0000018f-4fee-dc9e-a7df-4ffe493a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙是否违反了国际法？布林肯本周必须回答的关键问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-must-answer-by-wednesday-is-israel-complying-with-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-4df5-d17f-adcf-fdf791dc0000</link><description>随着以色列违背美国意愿准备对拉法采取地面行动，而以色列和哈马斯正在逐步接近达成停火和人质协议，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯必须在周三之前告诉国会他是否接受以色列的保证使用美国武器时不得违反国际法</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 20:02:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-must-answer-by-wednesday-is-israel-complying-with-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-4df5-d17f-adcf-fdf791dc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>